<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      You've been added as a learner to the <%= @badge.name %> badge in Badge List. 
      This badge is part of the <%= @group.name %> learning group.
      To begin adding entries to your learning log you can login to Badge List as normal or click on the link below.
    </p>
    <p>
      <strong>Your Learning Log / Personal Wiki:</strong> 
      <%= link_to group_badge_log_url(@group, @badge, @log), 
        group_badge_log_url(@group, @badge, @log) %> <br>
      <strong><%= @badge.name %>:</strong> 
      <%= link_to group_badge_url(@group, @badge), group_badge_url(@group, @badge) %> 
      (You were added by <%= @from_user.name %>.)
    </p>
    <p>
      <i>
        This email was sent automatically by the Badge List app.
        Badge List is a badge-based tool for tracking learning progress. 
        If you take no action you will not receive any further emails about this change.
      </i>
    </p>
  </body>
</html>